Indeed, the collaboration between public and private sectors in developing user-friendly mobile applications is a testament to the power of synergy. The success of the Meteo.lt app is a perfect example of how combining the best practices from both sectors can lead to innovative solutions that meet user needs effectively. I have had the opportunity to work on similar projects where the integration of public weather data and user-centric design has significantly enhanced user experience and engagement.

As the industry evolves, it becomes increasingly important to not only adopt new technologies